CriteriaAll the candidates must fulfill the following eligibility criteria to apply online for Vridhavastha Pension Yojana. Below is the complete procedure to check eligibility:- Mukhyamantri Vridhjan Samman Pension Yojana EligibilityCandidates have to visit the official website rajssp.raj.nic.inAt the homepage, click at the \u201cEligibility Criteria\u201d section in the header.To avail pension, the annual income of the family of the applicant must not exceed Rs. 48,000 per annumPension For Women \u2013 Women belonging to the age group of 55 to 75 years will get Rs. 750 per month while women having age of 75 years or above will get Rs. 1000 per month.Pension For Men \u2013 Men belonging to the age group of 58 to 75 years will get Rs. 750 per month while men of 75 years or above will get Rs. 1000 per month.All the pensioners can check their eligibility criteria through the Bhamashah Details. Moreover, pensioners can check their eligibility through Gender, Category, Marital Status, Age, BPL Type & other details.All the candidates will have to fill the application form and then submit the completed application form to Social Welfare Officer in District / Taluka in Rajasthan. All the approved applicants will start receiving the pension amount.\u0935\u0943\u0926\u094d\u0927\u093e\u0935\u0938\u094d\u0925\u093e \u092a\u0947\u0902\u0936\u0928 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0924\u0939\u0924 \u0926\u0940 \u091c\u093e\u0928\u0947 \u0935\u093e\u0932\u0940 \u092a\u0947\u0902\u0936\u0928 \u0930\u093e\u0936\u093f \u0915\u094b \u0939\u092e\u0928\u0947 \u092a\u094d\u0930\u0924\u093f\u092e\u093e\u0939 500 \u0930\u0941\u092a\u090f \u0938\u0947 \u092c\u0922\u093c\u093e\u0915\u0930 750 \u0930\u0941\u092a\u090f \u0924\u0925\u093e 750 \u0930\u0941\u092a\u090f \u0938\u0947 \u092c\u0922\u093c\u093e\u0915\u0930 1 \u0939\u091c\u093e\u0930 \u0930\u0941\u092a\u090f \u0915\u093f\u092f\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964\u2014 Ashok Gehlot (@ashokgehlot51) December 29, 2018These applicants c